---

<BlogArticleLayout
  title="Peptides for Women: What the Evidence Actually Shows"
  seoTitle="Peptides for Women: The Evidence"
  subtitle="Most articles about peptides for women just add the word 'women' to a list studied in men. This one asks the narrower, useful question: for a specific compound, in women, at what life stage, what does the evidence show — and is it legal to obtain?"
